#### Release Branches
```bash
# Branch
release/COP-202-v1.2.3-release

# Commits
COP-202 Prepare release v1.2.3 with new features
COP-202 Update version numbers and changelog
COP-202 Final testing and bug fixes for release
```

### Git Workflow Integration
- **Branch Creation**: Always create branches from `master` with proper naming
- **Commit Frequency**: Make small, focused commits with clear messages
- **Pull Request**: Use branch name as PR title, expand in description
- **Merge Strategy**: Use squash and merge to maintain clean history
- **Release Tags**: Tag releases with version numbers (e.g., `v1.2.3`)

### Quality Assurance for Git Operations
- **Pre-commit Checks**: Run linting and type checking before committing
- **Build Verification**: Ensure build passes before pushing
- **Test Verification**: Run tests to ensure functionality works
- **Message Review**: Verify commit message follows naming conventions
- **Branch Naming**: Confirm branch name includes Jira ticket number

### Common Patterns to Avoid
```bash
# ❌ Avoid - No Jira ticket
git commit -m "Fix bug in step editing"
git commit -m "Add new feature"

# ❌ Avoid - Generic messages
git commit -m "COP-123 Update files"
git commit -m "COP-123 Fix issues"

# ❌ Avoid - Past tense
git commit -m "COP-123 Added filter functionality"

# ❌ Avoid - Too verbose
git commit -m "COP-123 Implemented comprehensive filter functionality with multiple options and validation"

# ✅ Correct - Clear and specific
git commit -m "COP-123 Add filter functionality to step editing"
git commit -m "COP-123 Fix step deletion causing process corruption"
git commit -m "COP-123 Extract icon components for better reusability"
```

### Branch Naming Patterns to Avoid
```bash
# ❌ Avoid - No Jira ticket
feature/add-filters
bugfix/step-deletion
hotfix/critical-issue

# ❌ Avoid - No prefix
COP-123-add-filter-functionality
COP-123-fix-step-deletion-bug
COP-123-implement-custom-tabs

# ❌ Avoid - Unclear naming
feature/COP-123-fix
fix/COP-123-update
feature/COP-123-changes

# ❌ Avoid - Wrong prefix for the type of work
fix/COP-123-add-new-feature  # Should be feature/
feature/COP-123-fix-bug      # Should be fix/

# ✅ Correct - Clear and descriptive with proper prefix
feature/COP-123-add-filter-functionality
fix/COP-123-fix-step-deletion-bug
feature/COP-123-implement-custom-tabs
release/COP-202-v1.2.3-release
```

### Integration with Development Workflow
- **Jira Integration**: Link commits to Jira tickets for better tracking
- **Code Review**: Use commit messages to understand changes quickly
- **Release Notes**: Generate release notes from commit messages
- **Bug Tracking**: Easily trace bugs back to specific commits
- **Feature History**: Track feature development through commit history

### Tools and Automation
- **Commit Hooks**: Use pre-commit hooks to enforce message format
- **Branch Protection**: Protect main branches and require PR reviews
- **Automated Testing**: Run tests on all commits and PRs
- **Release Automation**: Automate releases based on commit messages
- **Changelog Generation**: Auto-generate changelogs from commit messages
